5|$|The company's {{initial public}} {{offering}} was held on March 14, 1986. The stock, which eventually closed at US$27.75 a share, peaked at $29.25 a share shortly after the market opened for trading. After the offering, Microsoft had a market capitalization of $519.777 million. Microsoft has subsequently acquired 207 companies, purchased stakes in 64 companies, and made 25 divestments. Of the companies <b>that</b> <b>Microsoft</b> has acquired, 107 were based in the United States. Microsoft has not released financial details for most of these mergers and acquisitions.|$|E
